# Prompt Files

Store project prompts under `.prompts/`.

Rules:

- keep numbering strictly monotonic
- keep one dominant goal per prompt
- reference exact repo paths such as `{{starter_route_path}}` and `{{starter_test_path}}`
- do not renumber historical prompts after follow-up work

Suggested sequence:

1. `001-bootstrap-repo.txt`
2. `002-refine-test-surface.txt`

